item.title: About
item.description:
My name is Nhat Dao and I love Computer Science and Mathematics. In my freetime, I am generally found trying out new programming languages or jamming with my guitar and my keyboard.

I am currently in my senior year at UT Arlington. Beside school, I’m also an officer and mentor at Mobi
